            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>ublio</ex></expan> Nonio Asprenate <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> Aquila Iuliano <lb n="3"/>co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Kalab</abbr><ex>rum</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>nf</ex><abbr>usum</abbr></expan> in <expan><abbr>amp</abbr><ex>horam</ex></expan> |(congios) X <lb n="5"/>vindemia <lb n="6"/>Paulli co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulis</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>H</abbr><ex>elvius</ex></expan><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">B(asila)</supplied>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zwei aneinanderpassende Fragmente einer Amphore (Dressel 6A). Schreibtechnik: Z. 1-5: Dipinto (schwarze Tinte); Z. 6: gestempelt. Z. 3: hinter Z. 1/2, etwa auf Höhe des Zwischenraums zwischen Z. 1 u. 2 platziert. Z. 6: vom H(?) nur das obere Ende der linken senkrechten Haste erhalten; Ergänzungsvorschlag nach Piccottini.</p>
            </div>
